$ /sys/class/power_supply/BAT0/capacity

Apparently, this »file« shows the percentage of the fullness of a laptop's battery.

Watching the battery getting charged:
code {
$ → Linux/shell/commands/watch --interval=5 cat  /sys/class/power_supply/BAT0/capacity
code }


sa:
  → Linux/Laptop#linux-battery-status

  → Linux/fhs/sys/class/power_supply/BAT0/
